    <h3 id="troubleshooting">Troubleshooting</h3>
    <p>Guacbot prints a lot of debugging messages to the console, especially when there is an 
    unexpected condition. In additional, errors should provide a stack trace. All of this information
    is critical to debugging any issues you may encounter. If you think you are experiencing a bug,
    please provide all of the console output when <a href="//github.com/prgmrbill/guacbot/issues/new">opening an issue</a>. 
    Please include steps to reproduce the problem. </p>
